{"tid":1550440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傻閪差佬 你知唔知點解唔成立獨立調查委員會呀","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:58:19.000Z","uid":8478,"like":136,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"8a937126ba5782cbc8601e9f132b2c4cee623935","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會調查曬成件事 即係會有官員落鑊<br />\n依家監警會查 即係只會拎你班狗去煲狗肉咋傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為監警會廢？呢單嘢搞成咁 點會唔拎你地班狗出嚟祭旗呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你寧願同官員攬炒定自己揹曬 你地自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知你地可能讀書唔多 俾班高層説兩説就以為獨立調查係害你地<br />\n但你諗下你坐監班高官高層會唔會同你地坐先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b4c61dcbc1467d14d6319b2bd21a8412839018","tid":1550440,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e5e6e22485b7e0dac130179034b802d09c74906","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"狗仔你地好得意 應承我唔好變成狗肉煲啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變都拎埋隻鵝一齊抆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc15f3e1d6345be2c99a7a9ab33017a529a4209a","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:08:46.000Z","msg":"救救狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef429c483b3193f990d1eafb859e985d47fe5c9","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:12:57.000Z","msg":"柒鵝已經退咗一步啦 下一步就輪到你地啦 你地甘心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77797ed6530e49a1d8fe9648738c3b23d6196fb7","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6781049751cba3f004fd67f9bb4e8b991a0a5a94","tid":1550440,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"炒警狗高層好撚過狗仔喇, 反正都無限, 又無號碼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ffa9f3120ae66ed167fa27b164e5a0a70e5cb8","tid":1550440,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"終於有人講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4660c4b57ab839d6a4e5c39928a9c8a6eabbe882","tid":1550440,"uid":26385,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"丫屌又好似係喎<br />\n獨立調查就係查大粒，查邊個落order<br />\n監警就...你自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f8843227860f54b78fd8b3a5f00080a6ccee1c","tid":1550440,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce9dff37a6a2182b49df9761ae599c82782fbb3","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"所以唔成立獨立調查委員會真係政府立場嚟<br />\n推到俾愛協知有人打算串謀虐待動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda747a28d3bf2be905c3211f5d45e02c5dc89d8","tid":1550440,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"若然未報，時辰未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，遮打見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZUq8PfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUq8PfJ.png&h=6ed8457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外以下口號可以一記：<br />\n-Free Hong Kong, Democracy now!<br />\n-Fight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong!<br />\n-Five Demands, Not one less!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">練定美國國歌一齊唱K</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=fac253d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a>"},{"pid":"d0d9fb80440b6a0870d2ae7be85c26d68344353b","tid":1550440,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"POPO有智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339718273e381a4d13c6a100eb51a268fc20074f","tid":1550440,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683dbaf8f2d32d418e02d27e11567ffa220cd48e","tid":1550440,"uid":48315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"監警會無調查權<br />\n但睇下片都可以郁9你班前線 再搵法庭判<br />\n你地咪繼續打囉<br />\n搵5個外國人入黎都係想由佢地做9班前線<br />\n廢事有建制9奶野<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得朱經緯同7警(仲要有部份人影唔到樣都殺埋)都係得條片<br />\n然後係由監警會郁9佢地"},{"pid":"a21cb04313965dd2b5a8432af435454c89f61242","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔好以為冇編號就查你唔到<br />\n如果唔係冇編號冇糧出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980a1174f6850b7a03deb311125ee7d7da098efc","tid":1550440,"uid":48315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a21cb04313965dd2b5a8432af435454c89f61242","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔好以為冇編號就查你唔到<br />\n如果唔係冇編號冇糧出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"跟本就係睇高層想郁邊個就供條友出黎<br />\n班前線狗仲以為高層會保佢 都ON99<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查就係郁高層同官<br />\n你班毅進仔受指令點會郁到你地<br />\n<br />\n所以弱智真係無我救<br />\n以為無獨立調查自己就會無事"},{"pid":"53cbef74dcf293009ed44ea7666b478594f3c1e7","tid":1550440,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"高官 高層想保自己炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估林鄭條7婆真係為左保你地"},{"pid":"b92d3b9342a0844263e98a4b94b79e64e0b1c534","tid":1550440,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:28:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有集會開始前，應先唱頌或奏《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n參加者應當起立，肅立致敬<br />\n右手置於心胸前<br />\n任何非宗教的頭飾應摘除並放置於左肩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQQpnEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQQpnEV.png&h=d7a5b483&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa8cebf712d1c2485a1547dd6ba5ef01f38c3215","tid":1550440,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a937126ba5782cbc8601e9f132b2c4cee623935","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會調查曬成件事 即係會有官員落鑊<br />\n依家監警會查 即係只會拎你班狗去煲狗肉咋傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為監警會廢？呢單嘢搞成咁 點會唔拎你地班狗出嚟祭旗呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你寧願同官員攬炒定自己揹曬 你地自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知你地可能讀書唔多 俾班高層説兩説就以為獨立調查係害你地<br />\n但你諗下你坐監班高官高層會唔會同你地坐先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"1fd57a9fbdb573b5ef69a9e8e6588193ecf192ca","tid":1550440,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"9月8點應對外國記者+資料整合+3首歌歌詞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dQkeqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dQkeqS</a>"},{"pid":"514d9b58670b24ab3e069a73108de255abc1dbf0","tid":1550440,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"起碼擺返幾百隻警犬祭旗先<br />\n<br />\nbtw 五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n堅決要求成立獨立調查委員會"},{"pid":"12e3b60f1d86dbf0669163a73bc03f81a33c0ffd","tid":1550440,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452152905c0fb8491f99a38f492aece33685830e","tid":1550440,"uid":195619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"啱呀~<br />\n前者查官查高層<br />\n後者只會交藍衫"},{"pid":"9d52ed75a1e575beb7e6dd